UNEXPECTED_STATE_PROMPT: Lantern è in uno stato inaspettato. Prova a ricaricare e, se il problema persiste, prova a chiudere e a riavviare. Puoi anche provare a reinstallare Lantern. Come ultimo tentativo scegliendo Reset si riporterà Lantern allo stato iniziale. Riportando qualsiasi informazione aggiuntiva agli sviluppatori di Lantern potrai accelerare la risoluzione del problema.
SETTINGS_UNLOCK_PROMPT: Inserisci la tua password di Lantern per sbloccare le impostazioni.
SETTINGS_LOAD_FAILURE_PROMPT: Your settings could not be loaded. Try again, and if the problem persists, try quitting and restarting. As a last resort, choosing Reset will reset Lantern to its original state. Reporting any additional information about the problem to the Lantern developers can speed its resolution.
UNEXPECTED_ERROR: Si è verificato un errore inaspettato.

BETA_STATEMENT: Lantern is beta software, which means it hasn’t yet been tested enough to be ready for large-scale distribution. Thank you for your help testing Lantern, and for understanding wherever it’s still rough around the edges. Also remember that Lantern is pending external security audit and thorough peer review within the technical community. Please only use Lantern if you understand your risks.

We have an explicit interest in keeping any personally identifiable information routed through Lantern servers and clients limited, secret, and ephemeral. All Lantern software and infrastructure has been configured with strong security protections and data expungement policies in accordance with that interest. For more information, please see https://github.com/getlantern/lantern/wiki/Privacy.
